  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851930/extras/a66d7031d459bc0e5b50f6f40de930fe.poster.avif?t=1725191230\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851930/extras/a66d7031d459bc0e5b50f6f40de930fe.webm?t=1725191230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851930/extras/a66d7031d459bc0e5b50f6f40de930fe.mp4?t=1725191230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Design and build arenas for your guests to fight in, keep them happy, your workers paid and make a profit!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851930/extras/b8c127085190cad661518d3b5ed05ebc.poster.avif?t=1725191230\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851930/extras/b8c127085190cad661518d3b5ed05ebc.webm?t=1725191230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851930/extras/b8c127085190cad661518d3b5ed05ebc.mp4?t=1725191230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851930/extras/1e0133502c2d978cd4aa63accf9e33e0.avif?t=1725191230\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><strong>Design</strong> and build your own arenas for your guests to fight.<br><strong>Set up</strong> the Arena rules and Game Mode: Battle Royale, Team Deathmatch, Capture the Flag.<br><strong>Listen</strong> to your guests and improve the design of your arenas: Add guns, cover, fix spawn kills.<br><strong>Build</strong> up the rest of your park with Shops, Bathrooms, Shooting Ranges, etc.<br><strong>Repair</strong> your items and keep them in good condition so no one gets hurt.<br><strong>Clean</strong> up the arenas before starting a new battle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851930/extras/1a06c8065c9212d5eb437af6961e1fb5.poster.avif?t=1725191230\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851930/extras/1a06c8065c9212d5eb437af6961e1fb5.webm?t=1725191230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851930/extras/1a06c8065c9212d5eb437af6961e1fb5.mp4?t=1725191230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Keep your Guests happy, your Workers busy and make a profit!</strong></h2>",
